---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Really Important Facts About Bitcoin">
  <Header />

  <main class="main-content">
    <div class="content-container">
      <h1>10 Bitcoin Facts</h1>
      <ol>
        <li>
          Bitcoin is not a company, it doesn't have a CEO, and <strong>can't go bankrupt</strong>.
        </li>
        <li>
          There will only ever be 21 million bitcoin, millions have already been lost forever. It's
          the <strong>scarcest thing in the world</strong>.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>No one knows who invented Bitcoin</strong>, Bitcoin's creator, Satoshi Nakamoto,
          has never been found.
        </li>
        <li>
          Bitcoin was inspired by decades of research into money and cryptography, and the Great
          Financial Crisis of 2008. <strong>Bitcoin was designed to help everyday people</strong>.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>Bitcoin and Crypto are different</strong>. People often confuse them, if you want
          to buy real bitcoin you need to make sure you're buying something with the ticker "BTC".
        </li>
